Community
No man is an island. At Welch Hornsby, we believe we are all connected. Our commitment to our clients fuels our commitment to our communities. Our commitment to our clients is uncompromising. It is with the same passion that we serve our fellow man. We recognize the gifts we have been given. And we also recognize our responsibility to share these gifts. Welch Hornsby, collectively and individually, is active in a variety of causes that touch the lives of those around us.
We serve as board members or acting members in the following organizations:
